          %p
            %strong Calepin is closing shop.
            The blogging service I use for this here blog is called
            %a{:href => "http://calepin.co/"} Calepin,
            and I like it a lot (as
            %a{:href => "http://carlo.zottmann.org/2012/01/20/the-big-blog-move-of-2012/"} mentioned before
